'''嗜中性白血球低下症'''（Neutropenia 或 Neutropaenia），亦称中性粒細胞減少症，是血液中的一種[[中性粒細胞|中性粒細胞]]（一種白血球細胞）濃度異常低的血液系統疾病<ref>{{Cite web|title = Neutropenia - National Library of Medicine|url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0025031/|website = PubMed Health|accessdate = 2015-12-08|first = National Center for Biotechnology|last = Information|first2 = U. S. National Library of Medicine 8600 Rockville|last2 = Pike|first3 = Bethesda|last3 = MD|first4 = 20894|last4 = Usa}}</ref>，中性粒細胞彌補大多數的循環白血球，和透過破壞[[細菌|細菌]]、細菌碎片、和血液中與[[免疫球蛋白|免疫球蛋白]]結合的病毒，作為對抗[[感染|感染]]的主要防護<ref>{{Cite web|title = Neutrophils - National Library of Medicine|url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0022058/|website = PubMed Health|accessdate = 2015-12-08|first = National Center for Biotechnology|last = Information|first2 = U. S. National Library of Medicine 8600 Rockville|last2 = Pike|first3 = Bethesda|last3 = MD|first4 = 20894|last4 = Usa|archive-date = 2018-03-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180306215841/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0022058/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，其特徵是[[白血球|白血球]]中的[[中性白血球|中性白血球]]數量過低。嗜中性白血球低下症患者的臨床特徵差異很大，可能完全沒有症狀，但更容易受到細菌感染，如沒有及時就醫，病情可能演變成為危及生命的「中性粒細胞減少敗血症」，或可能有嚴重的感染，造成嚴重的併發症以及死亡。

嗜中性白血球低下症可以是急性（臨時）或慢性（長期）的，這個名稱有時會跟白細胞減少症（Leukopenia）互換使用<ref>{{Cite journal|title = How to approach neutropenia|url = http://asheducationbook.hematologylibrary.org/content/2012/1/174|journal = ASH Education Program Book|date = 2012-12-08|issn = 1520-4391|pmid = 23233578|pages = 174–182|volume = 2012|issue = 1|doi = 10.1182/asheducation-2012.1.174|first = Laurence A.|last = Boxer|access-date = 2016-06-21|archive-date = 2019-08-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190812015140/http://asheducationbook.hematologylibrary.org/content/2012/1/174|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 定義 ==
人類周邊血液中，[[白血球|白血球]]數目的總數乘以嗜中性白血球所佔的比例，即為嗜中性白血球的數目。例如白血球的總數是6000/mm3，乘以嗜中性白血球的比例是60%，嗜中性白血球的數目就是3600/mm3。嗜中性白血球的數目若低於1500/mm3，稱為輕度嗜中性白血球低下(mild neutropenia)。嗜中性白血球的數目若低於1000/mm3，稱為中度嗜中性白血球低下(moderate neutropenia)。嗜中性白血球的數目若低於500/mm3，稱為重度嗜中性白血球低下(severe neutropenia)<ref name="#1"> Wintrobe's Clinical Hematology </ref>。 在西元1966年，Bodey 等人證實嗜中性白血球減少的程度以及減少持續的時間和造成感染的風險有直接相關 <ref> Bodey GP, Buckley M, Sathe YS, Freireich EJ. Quantitative relationships between circulating leukocytes and infection in patients with acute leukemia. Ann Intern Med. 1966 Feb;64(2):328-40. PMID 5216294 </ref>。

== 癥狀 ==
嗜中性白血球低下症的癥狀與症狀一致的包括：發燒、吞嚥痛、牙齦痛、皮膚[[膿瘍|膿瘍]]、耳炎。患者出現這些症狀往往由於患者受到感染<ref>{{Cite web|title = Neutropenia Clinical Presentation: History, Physical Examination|url = http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/204821-clinical|website = emedicine.medscape.com|accessdate = 2015-12-08|archive-date = 2020-09-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923145638/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/204821-clinical|dead-url = no}}</ref>。兒童患者可能會出現[[應激性|應激性]]及吞嚥困難<ref>{{Cite book|title = Nursing Care of the Critically Ill Child|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=up93BAm-wNoC&pg=PA835&dq=neutropenia+symptoms&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjSoaLl38zJAhULqoMKHU-VAGgQ6AEINjAB#v=onepage&q=neutropenia%2520symptoms&f=false|publisher = Elsevier Health Sciences|date = 2012-05-04|page = 835|isbn = 0323086039|first = Mary Fran|last = Hazinski|access-date = 2016-06-21|archive-date = 2020-10-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201014135406/https://books.google.com/books?id=up93BAm-wNoC&pg=PA835&dq=neutropenia+symptoms&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjSoaLl38zJAhULqoMKHU-VAGgQ6AEINjAB#v=onepage&q=neutropenia%2520symptoms&f=false|dead-url = no}}</ref>，患者也被觀察到[[低血壓|低血壓]]的情況。

